<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Upper Mount Royal </h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Formerly American Hill, Upper Mount Royal homes began as an enclave of American Business
                elite. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">Upper Mount Royal features luxury real estate in one of the wealthiest neighbourhoods in
                Calgary and is situated overlooking Elbow Park. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Lower Mount Royal is a more typical Calgary community consisting largely of lowrise condos
                and townhomes. One of Calgary’s older neighbourhoods, many of the Upper Mount Royal homes are an image
                of Calgary’s beginnings as a city, and where the men and women who made the city what it is today once
                lived.</p>

        </div>
